{
  "id": "adv_event_2511_01_03",
  "title": "リズノワ\nとの融合",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――翌朝",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "endTime": 1.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ameapart-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ameapart-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi Igawa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_03-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "ダメだ……あれから徹夜で考えてるのに、リズノワと\nインド映画の融合がどうしてもうまくいかない！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 1.9999999922,
      "endTime": 9.2666213911,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ameapart-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ameapart-00-noon",
      "startTime": 9.4666666588
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_03-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "でしょうね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.4666666588,
      "endTime": 10.7609530767,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro Akazaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_03-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "冷静に考えれば分かりますよ\nインド映画がリズノワに、合う訳ないじゃないですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.9759415945,
      "endTime": 17.476168378300002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ameapart-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ameapart-00-noon",
      "startTime": 17.6759415945
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi Igawa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_03-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "そうかな。僕はいけると思うけど。僕ら四人なら\nどんなジャンルだろうと歌いこなせるはずだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.6759415945,
      "endTime": 25.8759416898,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_03-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "頭ごなしに否定はしたくないけど……インド映画は\n演劇と歌と踊りが一体となった映像美が魅力でしょ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.0759415945,
      "endTime": 34.0549209913,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ameapart-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ameapart-00-noon",
      "startTime": 34.2699095091
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_03-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "ライブパフォーマンスを追求する私達とは方向性が\n違うわ。もっと他に合うものがあるんじゃないかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.2699095091,
      "endTime": 41.6771883331,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ameapart-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ameapart-00-noon",
      "startTime": 41.8921768508
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi Igawa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_03-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "そう……莉央がそう言うなら、そうなんだろうね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.8921768508,
      "endTime": 46.955781491799996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ameapart-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ameapart-00-noon",
      "startTime": 47.1588427546
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro Akazaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_03-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "どうしてこころの言葉は疑うのに、莉央さんに\n言われたらすぐ信じるんですか！　納得いきません！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.1588427546,
      "endTime": 53.4301352504,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ameapart-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ameapart-00-noon",
      "startTime": 53.6255094213
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai Komiyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_03-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "インド映画は一旦置いといて\n違う方向性も考えてみませんか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.6255094213,
      "endTime": 58.777187316,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ameapart-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ameapart-00-noon",
      "startTime": 58.9255101843
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai Komiyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_03-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "そうだ！　また温泉に行きましょう！\nリラックスすれば、きっといいアイデアが浮かびますよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.9255101843,
      "endTime": 65.5770521803,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ameapart-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ameapart-00-noon",
      "startTime": 65.7921768509
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi Igawa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_03-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "……そうだね。愛の言う通りにするよ\n温泉で新しいアイデアを考えよう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.7921768509,
      "endTime": 71.4588393532,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ameapart-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ameapart-00-noon",
      "startTime": 71.6588394486
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro Akazaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_03-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "どうしてこころの言葉は信じないのに、愛ちゃんの\n言葉は素直に聞くんですか！　納得いきません！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.6588394486,
      "endTime": 78.24021771780001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数時間後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.1588353797,
      "endTime": 80.2655025884,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 80.2655025884
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_03-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "葵ったら、急に温泉を飛び出して一人でどこに\n行ったのかしら。タオルも置き忘れてるし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.1255045895,
      "endTime": 88.8255046849,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 89.0404932027
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro Akazaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_03-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "いきなり「閃いた！」って叫んで出て行くなんて\n一体何があったんでしょう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.0404932027,
      "endTime": 94.6404995682,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 94.8071662349
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai Komiyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_03-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "あっ！　あそこで荷物を抱えて歩いてるのは\n葵さんじゃないですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.3404870992,
      "endTime": 100.4242738728,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5299.999999999997
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 100.6404870992
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi Igawa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_03-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "やあみんな。ちょうど良かった。買い物をしたんだけど\nみんなに見てほしいものがあるんだ。いいかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.6404870992,
      "endTime": 107.8316890721,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 108.0404870992
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_03-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "葵が持ってるのは……カスタネットと赤いバラ？\nえっ、いきなりバラの花を口に咥えて何をする気？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.0404870992,
      "endTime": 117.36715564779999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 117.5821441656
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi Igawa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_03-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "タン、タタタン、タンタン！　オーレ！\n……どうかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.5821441656,
      "endTime": 121.8821396357,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_castanets-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 119
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 120.5956391431
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 122.082139588
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai Komiyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_03-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "ええと……なんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.082139588,
      "endTime": 125.0877858645,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro Akazaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_03-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "愛ちゃん、分からないんですか？\nあれは情熱のダンス……フラミンゴです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.282139588,
      "endTime": 131.5289197928,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 131.7154729213
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai Komiyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_03-ai005.m4a",
      "text": "これが……フラミンゴ！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.7154729213,
      "endTime": 134.1754730071,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 134.382139588
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_03-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "フラメンコよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.382139588,
